{"tid":1781945,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我希望大家入嚟可以聽我呢個讀LLB既講幾句 － 關於終審法院","createTime":"2019-12-13T14:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T17:54:49.000Z","uid":97944,"like":39,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"25aa03cb653440714f3de72e0e8231e202684d17","tid":1781945,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:10:46.000Z","msg":"話說前兩日大家見到監警會國際專家因爲頂唔順政府而集體辭職：<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191213/_2019121306451762070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191213%2F_2019121306451762070.jpg&h=91f0792a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢批專家全部來自英聯邦國家 <br />\n大家又知唔知其實終審法院都有兩個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">來自英聯邦既前首席法官</span></strong>?<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/filemanager/biograhpy/tc/upload/61/A20191127E_TCH_0940%20small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fbiograhpy%2Ftc%2Fupload%2F61%2FA20191127E_TCH_0940%2520small.jpg&h=86f921b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/filemanager/biograhpy/tc/upload/60/Lady%20Hale%20(UKSC)%20smaller.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fbiograhpy%2Ftc%2Fupload%2F60%2FLady%2520Hale%2520%28UKSC%29%2520smaller.jpg&h=904ccbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上: Lady Justice McLachlin 加拿大最高法院前首席法官<br />\n下: Baroness Hale 英國最高法院前首席法官<br />\n（其實大家search下就知兩位都好猛料）<br />\n<br />\n香港司法界其實係今次制度暴力既幫兇之一<br />\n本身首席法官馬道立既判案立場已經好保守 <br />\n成日幫政府/權貴 <br />\n佢地用既理由當然係甚麼司法唔應該干預行政 又會話要守護法治之類 <br />\n<br />\n但由6月到依家 香港法治已經係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">蕩然無存</span></strong>:<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逃犯條例嚴重破壞香港法治</span></span></strong> 連兩個律師公會（包括大律師公會）都屌<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警犯晒法但係無一個受法律制裁</span></strong></span>，律政司視而不見<br />\n3. 好多被捕人士無得見律師(right to lawyer denied)，喺警署被虐打被屈，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警無視法律程序</strong></span></span><br />\n4. 好多等住見被捕者既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">律師比黑警恐嚇</span></strong></span>，話會被控非法集結<br />\n5. 政府違憲動用緊急法立反蒙面法<br />\n6. 反蒙面法一判咗違憲，大陸官方即刻出嚟屌，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重違反基本法司法獨立同審判權</span></span></strong><br />\n仲有好多好多好多<br />\n<br />\n而終審法院既法官由六月開始，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無出過一句聲</span></strong></span>！<br />\n大把人講過其實如果佢地<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">威脅林鄭集體辭職</span></strong>(只係威脅唔洗真做)，<br />\n逃犯條例就會撤回，<br />\n就唔會有之後半年既事<br />\n換言之，其實<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足們係幫緊呢班法官埋單</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更重要既係，呢班法官(包括上述嗰兩個外國法官)係一直幫政權背書！<br />\n佢地既沉默正正係對普通法最大既侮辱 <br />\n源自英國既普通法係唔可以咁樣比呢班法官咁樣禍害! <br />\n真係想守護法治既法官<br />\n應該辭職同政權畫清界線<br />\n<br />\n所以我打呢篇文既目的:<br />\n1. 比大家再一次了解下法律界既虛偽<br />\n2. 推比負責國際戰線既手足，起碼同英美加解釋翻香港法治已經崩壞<br />\n3. 甚至遊說呢啲英聯邦國家召回呢批法官</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都覺得係既，可以襯呢幾日無太多行動post幫手推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6178cc6801dcf9fbd9a13aa5c99e163f60716c44","tid":1781945,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e994d3c34ffdc93567df97946e29dc56d4662c","tid":1781945,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b030000a2c2de5ef07a41093f22dcb6653bfeb","tid":1781945,"ui